<h1>Solar Panel Cleaning Robot</h1>

<h2>Description</h2>

Designed and developed an autonomous solar panel cleaning robot inspired by the Ecoppia H4 cleaning system. The robot utilized a microfiber helix mechanism and vision-based navigation to provide efficient waterless cleaning.

<br />

<h2>Project Objectives</h2>

- Automate solar panel cleaning
- Reduce water consumption
- Improve cleaning efficiency
- Develop autonomous navigation

<h2>Process</h2>

- Designed robot structure
- Developed cleaning mechanism
- Integrated sensors and controllers
- Implemented navigation system
- Tested cleaning performance

